{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Desktop Cate Cafe is a <strong>cute, idle management game</strong> that lives at the bottom of your screen letting you work on other tasks while your cafe runs. Design your dream cafe, unlock delicious recipes, and automate your cafe by hiring cute cat staff!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/Sequence_01_20.gif?t=1738638898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Design Your Outdoor Cafe</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build the perfect cafe with hundreds of customization options paired with an easy to use building system that lets your creativity shine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/0_DCC_GIF_3_2.gif?t=1738638898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Unlock Delicious Recipes</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Progress by serving customers to unlock over 150 different recipes from colorful bubble tea to mouthwatering matcha cake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/DCC_Cakes_5.png?t=1738638898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Automate with Cute Staff</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire cute cat staff to take care of the cafe while you're gone or working on other tasks! Desktop Cat cafe sits comfortably at the bottom of your screen so you can always keep your customers happy.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978180/extras/FINAL_GIF_3.gif?t=1738638898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Desktop Cat Cafe is inspired by titles such as Rusty's Retirement and Minami Lane.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.a